1935;;Way Down East;;American;;Henry King;;Henry Fonda, Rochelle Hudson, Margaret Hamilton;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Way_Down_East_(1935_film);;The story centers upon a starving, impoverished gamin who lost everything after a wicked millionaire tricked her into a marriage and impregnated her. The baby doesn't survive the ordeal and the poor girl ends up sheltered by a puritanical farm family. While there, she falls in love with the son.[1]